window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>We're finally scouting out the great Sanctuary cities, magical spaceships big enough to host a dozen New Yorks.</b></p> <p>We just have to figure out how to turn them on, and we might have a way to save the people of Earth.</p> <p>On top of that, we're ready to hit the world dungeon to kick our power up to the next tier.</p> <p>All in all, things are going great.</p> <p>So, of course, the M'tari declare war on the Aetherium's great sky city, Aethireâ€”the same Aethire that has the world dungeon.</p> <p>Despite our best efforts, I can't stop myself... When people are in need, it seems I can't help but <i>To Stand Between Sea and Sky</i>.</p>"; 
